headline: This Growth Stock Is Crushing the Market This Year
summary: Dollar General has been outperforming the S&P 500 so far in 2025 by a wide margin.  One stock, however, that has soundly outperformed the broad index this year is Dollar General (NYSE: DG).  Is now really a good time to invest in Dollar General?
